      "Portugal is one of Europe's most romantic destinations, and there's no better way to celebrate your relationship than with a professional couples photoshoot. Whether you're exploring Lisbon's golden-lit streets hand in hand, watching the sunset over Porto's Douro River, or strolling through Sintra's fairytale gardens, our photographers know exactly how to capture the magic between you. Sessions start from €150 for 60 minutes and include 40-60+ professionally edited photos. No awkward posing — just natural, beautiful moments guided by someone who knows Portugal's most intimate and photogenic spots. Most couples book golden hour sessions for the warmest, most flattering light.",
